headline: QUALCOMM INC (NASDAQ:QCOM): A Strong Candidate for Sustainable Dividend Income
summary: QUALCOMM (QCOM) offers a solid dividend yield backed by strong earnings power and a decade of payout growth, making it a candidate for sustainable passive income.
